  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Yllas Log Cabins are self-catering cabins, each cabin has an equipped kitchen and dining room table. The nearby supermarket is well stocked, and is open until 9pm (times to be confirmed locally).</p>
<p>If you would rather have your meals included, there is an optional pre-bookable half board supplement for buffet breakfast and 3 course buffet dinner, taken at the Akas (Snow Elf) Hotel.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast, a Christmas celebration meal with games and music, is included on the final night of your holiday. Please note that the Festive Feast will replace your last half-board dinner. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
